text:
耳邊傳來[redacted_name]低沉的笑聲，卻充滿了濃濃的惡意:“才親你幾下就濕了？ 這身子可真夠淫蕩的……其實你是不是早就期待我這麼做了？ 所以才每天那麼殷勤的給我送早餐，就是希望被我操吧？”
“嗯啊……季……[redacted_name]……你……混蛋……”[redacted_name]嗚咽出聲，紅唇微張，渾身顫抖不已，一半是被[redacted_name]的忽然襲擊給弄的，一半是因為他所說的羞辱人的話語。
“哦？ 我混蛋？” [redacted_name]的眼神變得可怕無比，他冷冷一笑:“看來你是不見棺材不掉淚。”
trans:
[redacted_name]'s low laughter came to ears, but it was full of malice: "I've only kissed you a few times and you're already wet? This body is so naughty...Actually, have you been expecting me to do this for a long time?" ? That’s why you serve me breakfast so diligently every day, just because you want to be fucked by me, right?”
"Yeah... Ji... [redacted_name]... you... fucker... [redacted_name] whimpered, her red lips slightly opened, and her whole body was shaking, half caused by [redacted_name]'s sudden attack, and half It was because of the humiliating words he spoke.
"Oh? Am I a fucker?" [redacted_name]'s eyes became extremely scary, and he smiled coldly: "It seems that you won't shed tears until you see the coffin."
